Bombcats: Special Edition - it is a beautiful and fun arcade game about the adventures of cats. If we consider the concept of development is more exact, all of your favorite furry creatures in the game act as projectiles (bombs). We have to shoot bombs at such unusual obstacles that will meet us on the levels. Of the main features bombkats Specia edition would like to highlight: a bright and lush graphics, thoughtful gameplay with tons of levels, cool music, and charming protagonists.
